      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well cared for over the years. It's been so reliable for me, and I know it'll be the same for you! Perfect for someone looking for a solid daily driver that still looks great in the driveway. I\u2019m looking for a smooth sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
