      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and maintains a linear power curve up to the 8,400 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including treated rod bearings and upgraded throttle valve actuators, ensuring the longevity of the valvetrain and VANOS system. The chassis retains its composure with factory-spec bushings and a functional M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its age, the hydraulic steering rack remains communicative and the suspension geometry is true. A purist-spec driver with a clean service history.",
