      "description": "This 2018 BMW 330i xDrive offers a refined driving experience for those who value both performance and presentation. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Mineral Grey Metallic that holds a deep, reflective gloss; while there are a few minor rock chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper, the body remains straight and free of major dents. Inside, the Black Dakota leather upholstery is in excellent shape, showing minimal bolster wear and no punctures or fading. The cabin has been kept smoke-free and the dual-zone climate control, power moonroof, and Harman Kardon premium audio system all operate as they should. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust, backed by a consistent service history. It recently received a fresh oil change, new brake pads, and a set of four Michelin Pilot Sport tires with plenty of tread remaining. The 2.0L turbocharged engine pulls cleanly, and the 8-speed automatic transmission shifts with precision. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for the road.",
